parameters.description:
Granularity of time. Can be "oneminute", "fiveminutes", "hourly", "daily", or "monthly".
If the time range is no more than one day, the default value is "oneminute";
If the time range is more than one day but less than or equal to one week, the default value is "fiveminutes";
If the time range is more than one week but less than or equal to one month, the default value is "hourly";
If the time range is more than one month, the default value is "daily"; 
Restriction:
1.	One minute - Maximum time range is 7 days
2.	5 minutes - Maximum time range is 1 month(31d)
3.	Hourly, Daily, Monthly - Maximum time range is 1 year(366d)

